I"‡<h2 id="installation">Installation</h2>
<p>Download Poet from the <a href="https://chrome.google.com/webstore/detail/poet/hkjjflfleaejocakemkheofjcmkepbcm"> Chrome extension web store.</a></p>

<p align="center">
Displays a new poem every day.
